snippet.title: The Dark Matter mobile game
snippet.description:
The most intense and addicting arcade indie game, soon in stores!
WILL BE A TOTAL LOWPOLY BLAST!
The Dark Matter is aiming to be an Hit in 2017 in his simple gameplay and hard challenge! 

Twitter: https://twitter.com/DarkMatter_Game
PreApps: http://www.preapps.com/new-iphone-ipad-apps/the-dark-matter/5753  (Upvote and ask for Beta )

Music and SFX of the game by Victor Love
